From 3432c7a7535d3277e73e587067aef7bdd4e324e4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Juniper Bevensee <juniperbevensee@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 25 May 2026 11:51:37 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 21/27] refactor: convert boot.md from builtin hook to
 standalone plugin

Eliminates the HIGH-risk rebase patch on hooks.py by moving boot.md
functionality to plugins/boot_md/ with standard plugin registration.
Reverts _register_builtin_hooks() to its empty upstream state.

- New plugin at plugins/boot_md/ with plugin.yaml and register(ctx)
- Uses on_session_start hook instead of gateway:startup event
- Deleted gateway/builtin_hooks/boot_md.py (replaced by plugin)
- Moved tests to tests/plugins/test_boot_md_plugin.py (8 tests, all pass)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
